ed9790fbadfb38e4d660eb1befd87e803d70dec04d936e8cd26def4a9c21240bb7cae8750ae3395aa4761e6738b9e346c86ba57761cfde30efe46d2cb459a7e4  minio.confd
f24c5b51ecd5da7409e258e37bbdf868fdc4c56a209e8979a929952a7d35cae0e6890925eccbe10202c5cca17e16873c2b431d4728066faceb5832fba3061636  minio-0.20200306.tar.gz"
